BEGIN:VEVENT
CATEGORIES:History
DESCRIPTION:Remember when hobbies were more than just a way to pass the ti
 me - they were a chance to push the limits? From making model planes with
  glue that gets you high\, to cooking up explosive rocket fuel in the bac
 kyard\, to strapping ourselves to homemade kites and launching into the u
 nknown\, these hands-on pursuits often came with a dangerous edge. It's a
  thrilling\, hair-raising trip back to the crafty obsessions that prove o
 ur hazardous history was never just a hobby.
DTEND:20260608T014200Z
DTSTAMP:20260614T011101Z
DTSTART:20260608T010000Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Hazardous History with Henry Winkler - 2x07 - Hobbies Gone Haywire
UID:NzbDrone_episode_41055
END:VEVENT
