BEGIN:VEVENT
CATEGORIES:National Geographic
DESCRIPTION:Antoni explores New York City’s most singular\, world-class ex
 periences and uncovers the best of a city where history and modern life c
 ollide. Escape to bold fusion cuisine\, mind-bending cocktails and a uniq
 ue twist on NYC-style pizza\, he discovers some of the remarkable people 
 and cultural influences that shape the place he calls home.
