BEGIN:VEVENT
CATEGORIES:National Geographic
DESCRIPTION:Antoni curates London’s most memorable experiences\, from Bric
 k Lane’s multicultural cuisine to a swim at Canary Wharf. He learns what 
 makes Big Ben’s Great Clock tick\, tastes a Sunday roast with a twist\, c
 limbs up to the top of The Shard\, explores Kew Gardens\, and dives into 
 London’s drag scene with the performers who bring it to life.
